On Halloween night, Robert was all dressed to go out trick or treating and waited for his Dad to take him out.  His father told him that he had talked to the lady who lived next door and she was hoping that her granddaughter could go trick or treating with them.  Robert thought it would be okay if she came along and they went to go pick her up.  Robert found out her name was Tessa.  He was happy to see that she was wearing a costume that looked like a kitten.  Their costumes would go well together.

