*B) "Helmets are for girls!  You're not cool if you wear a helmet!" and "What are you, scared?"
 C) "Did your mommy buy you that helmet?"  and "Helmets are for girls!  You're not cool if you wear a helmet!"
 D) "Quit being such a cry baby" and "What are you, scared?"


