silly. They were in the same class. Jane did not make fun of Sarah. She gave her a bandage
instead. It had a cat on it to match Sarah's shirt.

Sarah was still unhappy. She would not eat her lunch or play at recess. When Stephanie
tried to talk to her she frowned. Then Stephanie gave Sarah a bunny toy that she
