 A) Cat
 B) Pumpkin
 C) Bob
*D) Gob

4: multiple: Why did Bob throw Gob into the house?
 A) He chased the duck.
*B) Gob ate a pumpkin.
 C) He ate a potato.
 D) He got hungry.


